flags.alt: The flag of the Democratic Republic of the Congo has a sky-blue field with a yellow-edged red diagonal band that extends from the lower hoist-side corner to the upper fly-side corner of the field. A yellow boar's tusk encircling two yellow crossed namele leaves is centered in the triangle.
